  <brief_title>Knee Joint Icing and Knee-extension Strength</brief_title>
  <acronym>IS</acronym>
  <official_title>No Effect of Knee Joint Icing on Knee-extension Strength After Total Knee Arthroplasty. A Randomized Cross-over Study</official_title>
